Coast to Coast AM 2012.02.18 Self-Transformation &amp; Development

Host:	John B. Wells
Guests:	William Whitecloud, Howard Bloom

Self-help author William Whitecloud spoke about his book, The Magician's Way, in which he presents secrets to creating a wonder-filled magical life through inner 'alchemical' transformation.

In the first hour, multi-disciplinary scientist Howard Bloom commented on a proposed Space Launch System (SLS), and the future of the U.S. space program.

